{"tid":2023012,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有被熱狗苦主大聯民咁有冇被泛粉苦主大聯盟？","createTime":"2020-05-18T16:40:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T04:45:24.000Z","uid":198373,"like":33,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a2dc910aa08b144655862ed2774986fc2fccdaa5","tid":2023012,"uid":198373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T16:40:14.000Z","msg":"反熱狗一定要痴泛民班甩皮甩骨垃圾咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母個臭化爛狗濃胞閪，你唔諗下你地幾撚多仇家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n青政、本民前、民族黨、普羅又泛民呀？<br />\n呀唔係，係偽獨派吖嘛。<br />\n又可以開多個被偽獨苦主大聯盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我留意好耐，有堆人好撚鍾意打完篇文加hashtag <span style=\"color: blue;\">#我係分化 #我係熱狗 </span><br />\n<br />\n咁撚樣就有道德高地咁，省啲啦撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，唔會令你篇野嘅論點高班好多架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我打完篇文我又加返個<span style=\"color: gold;\">#我唔係分化 #我係泛粉 </span>咁樣夠唔夠型呀"},{"pid":"c629fb2cbbd80567c1347cf7c1714eaffa4249c9","tid":2023012,"uid":198373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T16:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3700f34fca72654db29ef3a493b9630b66ae7f00","tid":2023012,"uid":198373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T16:44:34.000Z","msg":"最後：天滅共黨 光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c06fe49654c34b373f124eed416af9a8ad4021","tid":2023012,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3700f34fca72654db29ef3a493b9630b66ae7f00","tid":2023012,"uid":198373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor